<section id="challenges-and-approach" class="py-18">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-normal font-[Industry] text-pale-turquoise mb-12">
      > Overcoming Common Startup Hurdles: Our Way_
    </h2>
    <div class="py-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/snail.png"
            alt="snail"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium italic mb-4">
          "My MVP is taking forever, and I'm burning cash."
        </h3>

        <p class="font-light">
          We prioritize rapid iteration and efficient development. A
          non-technical founder partnering with us can go from a validated idea
          to a scalable MVP in weeks, focusing on core features first to
          get user feedback without overspending.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
