        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/negative-dynamic.png"
            alt="negative-dynamic"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium italic mb-4">
          "I'm worried my current tech setup won't handle growth or is
          insecure."
        </h3>
        <p class="font-light">
          From day one, we build your infrastructure using DevOps best
          practices. This means your systems are designed for security, can
          scale predictably with user demand, and are managed efficiently,
          giving you peace of mind.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/road-worker.png"
            alt="road-worker"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-normal italic mb-4">
          "We're swamped with manual tasks instead of focusing on growth."
        </h3>
        <p class="font-light">
          We identify key repetitive processes and automate them: from code
          deployment to customer onboarding sequences. This frees up your team
          to innovate and focus on your core business objectives.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/artificial-intelligence.png"
            alt="artificial-intelligence"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-normal italic mb-4">
          "AI seems powerful, but how can my small startup actually use it?"
        </h3>
        <p class="font-light">
          We demystify AI. Through practical readiness assessments, we help you
          identify simple, high-impact AI tools that can be integrated into your
          MVP or operations without needing a massive data science team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

